reviewText: Cannot play on my Dell Inspiron 13 with Windows 10 because cant see the "Continue" key. How do I get support?
Kids loved it!!! Very well done.

An excellent resource for learning to read Hebrew! Children can watch animated characters playing out stories to reinforce letters and nekudos, play review games, and watch Rabbi Potash teaching nekudos to his class. Rabbi Potash is an absolutely masterful teacher. Children will be looking, laughing, and most of all - learning with these games and videos.
